  <brief_title>Effect of Steep Trendelenburg in Laparoscopic Surgery on IOP &amp; RNFL Thickness</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Steep Trendelenburg Position Used During Laparoscopic Surgery on Intraocular Pressure During Surgery and on the Retinal Nerve Fiber Thickness After Surgery</official_title>
  <sponsors>
